metadata.name: A Loyal Companion
metadata.description:
" He's been waiting for so long, so long
Waiting for his master to come home
He'll never give up, no matter how long it takes
He'll keep on waiting, no matter what it takes "

No matter who you are, what are you are doing, 
he / she never judges you , all they show is love.

Illustration style - OPI Moire illusion
Made with Illustrator and AE
